{"tid":147080,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"忍夠個on9屋企 打算離家出走 有咩要注意","createTime":"2017-03-07T15:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T16:48:14.000Z","uid":62278,"like":25,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da886f64c8aa03599aafe4567d6c034680baa803","tid":147080,"uid":62278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:12:35.000Z","msg":"借ac開post<br />\n<br />\n呢個咁嘅垃圾屋企，乜柒野都同我講錢<br />\n係咁同我講嗱嗱聲出黎做野比家用佢<br />\n啱啱考完dse 搵份summer做下都問我幾錢人工仲幫我計埋我搵幾多 要比幾多家用佢<br />\n真係屌你老母仆街含撚死啦你 唔知係唔係你生<br />\n<br />\n我讀書有幾認真你又睇唔到<br />\n淨係識話我廢 其實你小學程度仲廢<br />\n<br />\nbtw 已經打算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讀多幾年屎片 返工 <br />\n夠錢養自己之日 就係離家出走之時<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時候趁屋企無人 執好個喼就閃人<br />\n(朋友屋企人細細個就識 被收留嘅機會大 加上無打算黏飲黏食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n離家出走如果佢報警係咪都無我乎?<br />\n警察搵到我 去警處銷案就可以走人?<br />\n有無巴絲都想離開個狗竇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c4df964f3a28719a4d83941a63bef3289fb429","tid":147080,"uid":62278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:14:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"610f675867fc72a74cb1897d993fce01924944e8","tid":147080,"uid":62278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:17:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"579cb756942db9d60112f75602416e6745dad09a","tid":147080,"uid":62278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:17:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f58d593fc3f6033c5641607e33dcaa1c22d428c3","tid":147080,"uid":62278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"376dc02e147181e4dc13a96bf0ca38bfec844659","tid":147080,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:20:21.000Z","msg":"出面租層樓有幾貴你知唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /